(4, 58, 'ACCOMMODATION & RATES_ARTICLE', 'accomodation-rates-article', '<div class="container_16">\r\n<div class="grid_16">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="grid_5 alpha">\r\n<h2>booking form</h2>\r\n{loadposition booking}</div>\r\n<div class="grid_11 omega">\r\n<h2>book a stay at mjejane river lodge</h2>\r\n<img class="img4" src="images/MRL_Website-018.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<p class="marTop2">As the African bush weaves its magic spell, your senses will awaken as never before and you will soak up a host of new experiences that will feed your soul. You will hear the sounds of the African bush and its deafening silence - a silence that may suddenly be broken by the whooping of hyenas, the reverberating roar of a lion, the loud grunting of hippos, the majestic trumpeting of elephants or the peaceful call of the fish eagle.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wrapper marTop2">\r\n<div class="grid_8 alpha">\r\n<div class="grid_4 rates">\r\n<h2>rates</h2>\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="box2">\r\n<p>01/05/2014 till 31/08/2014</p>\r\n<p>Standard Room/Single</p>\r\n<span>R 2680.00</span>\r\n<p>Standard Room/Per Person Sharing</p>\r\n<span>R 1790.00</span>\r\n<p>Children 6-11 years</p>\r\n<span>R 895.00</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="box2">\r\n<p>01/05/2014 till 31/08/2014</p>\r\n<p>Standard Room/Single</p>\r\n<span>R 3405.00</span>\r\n<p>Standard Room/Per Person Sharing</p>\r\n<span>R 2270.00</span>\r\n<p>Children 6-11 years</p>\r\n<span>R 1135.00</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="box2">\r\n<p>01/05/2014 till 31/08/2014</p>\r\n<p>Standard Room/Single</p>\r\n<span>R 3405.00</span>\r\n<p>Standard Room/Per Person Sharing</p>\r\n<span>R 2270.00</span>\r\n<p>Children 6-11 years</p>\r\n<span>R 1135.00</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_5 config">\r\n<h2>room configuration</h2>\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="first">16 luxury rooms</li> \r\n<li>3 double rooms</li>\r\n<li>13 twin rooms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>standard room features</h2>\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>All rooms have en-suite bathrooms</li>\r\n<li>Room equipped with hair dryer, tea &amp; coffee station, mini bar fridge</li>\r\n<li>Private patio overlooking the serene waters of the Crocodile River</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>arrival and departure times</h2>\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<p>check in-14h00 checkout-10h00</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="h2text">Special Offers</h2>\r\n<div class="wrapper_special">\r\n<div class="box_offer">\r\n<p style="margin: 0px;">No current Specials</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="wrapper marTop6">\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<p>Rates per person per night and include accommodation, three meals, two game drives, TOMSA levy and VAT at 14% Rates exclude transfers, beverages and conservation levy for the Kruger National Park of R250.00 per person per night, subject to change.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="wrapper marTop6">\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<p>Child Policy</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Children 0 - 5 years of age - Free of charge when sharing with full paying adults</li>\r\n<li>Children 6 - 11 years of age - Pay published child rate when sharing with two full paying adults</li>\r\n<li>Full adult rate applicable if occupying their own room or when sharing with one adult</li>\r\n<li>Children: 12 years &amp; older occupy their own room and pay full adult rate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="wrapper marTop6">\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<p>Rates are quoted per person per night and include accommodation, three meals, two game drives, TOMSA levy and VAT at 14% Rates exclude transfers, beverages and conservation levy for the Kruger National Park of R250.00 per person per night, subject to change.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 2, '