(9, 76, 'Facilities', 'facilities', '<div class="facility">\r\n<h2>Facilities at Mjejane</h2>\r\n<h4>The following facilities are available on site:</h4>\r\n         <ul>\r\n                   <li>LUXURY ACCOMODATION</li>\r\n                            <li>AL-A-CARTE RESTAURANT</li>\r\n                            <li>GYM</li>\r\n                            <li>GAME DRIVES</li>\r\n                            <li>SWIMMING POOL</li>\r\n                            <li>HEALTH SPA</li>\r\n                            <li>TENTED BOMA</li>\r\n                            <li class="last">VIEWING DECKS</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    ', '', 1, 2, '2014-11-24 07:56:35', 939, '', '2014-12-20 05:21:42', 939, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-11-24 07:56:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 10, 1, '', '', 1, 34, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(10, 93, 'FactSheet', 'factsheet', '<div class="grid_8">\r\n<div class="grid_4"><img class="img1" src="images/factsheet1.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="grid_4"><img class="img1" src="images/factsheet2.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="grid_4"><img class="img1" src="images/factsheet3.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="grid_4"><img class="img1" src="images/factsheet4.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong><em>The Southern part of the Kruger National Park is renowned for its superb game viewing, but the select area of Mjejane Game Reserve has been a best kept secret in honour of its awesome beauty.</em></strong></p>\r\n<div class="factsheet">\r\n<div class="fact-heading">\r\n<h4><strong>LOCATION AND DIRECTIONS</strong></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fact-text">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>450 km from Johannesburg</li>\r\n<li>100 km from Kruger Mpumalanga International Airport</li>\r\n<li>100 km from Nelspruit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="heading"><strong>BY AIR:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Fly to KMIA, (the nearest airport).</p>\r\n<p class="heading"><strong>BY ROAD:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Access to the reserve is gained via the N4, approximately 2,5km past the town of Hectorspruit, on the left side between Malelane and Komatipoort, en route to Maputo and Swaziland. Malelane town has a host of convenience shops, medical facilities and garages 20 minutes away, and three major golf courses are between 15 – 30 minutes drive from Mjejane.</p>\r\n<p class="fact-bold"><strong>GPS: S 25 22 48.4 / E 31 43 06.9</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fact-heading">\r\n<h4><strong>ACCOMMODATION</strong></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fact-text">\r\n<table cellpadding="2px" border="1">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Room Type:</th>\r\n<th>Total Number:</th>\r\n<th>Doubles:</th>\r\n<th>Twins:</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Luxury Room</td>\r\n<td>15</td>\r\n<td>Y - 3</td>\r\n<td>Y – 12</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Guide Room</td>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>N</td>\r\n<td>Y</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>All rooms have en-suite bathrooms and are air-conditioned. They have hairdryers, tea and coffee making facilities, telephones, mini fridges and satellite TV. All rooms have a private patio overlooking the serene waters of the Crocodile River.</p>\r\n<p>Children of all ages are welcome at the lodge. Children 0 – 5 years stay complimentary when sharing with parents, not permitted on game drives. 6 – 11 years enjoy a 50% discount on the adult sharing rate, permitted on game drives at management discretion and pay full conservation levy. Children 12 years and older pay the full adult rate and are permitted on game drive.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fact-heading">\r\n<h4><strong>FACILITIES, SERVICES AND ACTIVITIES AT THE LODGE AND NEARBY</strong></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fact-text">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Swimming Pool, Bar, Boma and indoor dining</li>\r\n<li>Check in at 14h00 – Check out at 10h00</li>\r\n<li>Baby-sitting Facilities</li>\r\n<li>Morning game drives into the Kruger National Park, afternoon game drives on the Mjejane Reserve</li>\r\n<li>Wi-Fi is available in the lounge area</li>\r\n<li>Bird Watching</li>\r\n<li>Tiger Fishing and Golf - nearby</li>\r\n<li>Chimpanzee Sanctuary – nearby</li>\r\n<li>Elephant-back Safaris – nearby</li>\r\n<li>Agricultural Tours - nearby</li>\r\n<li>Beaches of Mozambique - nearby</li>\r\n<li>Kingdom of Swaziland - nearby</li>\r\n<li>Scenic Panorama Route - nearby</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="heading">Additional Information:</p>\r\n<p>Mjejane is located in a Malaria area. Conservation levies are applicable.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fact-heading">\r\n<h4><strong>RESERVATION AND CONTACT DETAILS</strong></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fact-text reserve">\r\n<p>PO Box 95, Hectorspruit, 1230, South Africa</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong> + 27 (0)13 792 7000 – <strong>F:</strong> + 27 (0)13 792 7020 – <strong>E:</strong> reservations@mjejaneriverlodge.co.za – <strong>W:</strong> www.mjejaneriverlodge.co.za</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>RESERVATION DETAILS:</em></strong> <strong>T:</strong> + 27 (0)11 516 4367 <strong>| E:</strong> res@extraordinary.co.za/ res1@extraordinary.co.za</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 2, '2014-12-20 03:55:44', 939, '', '2014-12-20 05:21:58', 939, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-12-20 03:55:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 14, 0, '', '', 1, 35, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '');

