Scenic Panorama Route - nearby<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p class=\\"heading\\">Additional Information:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Mjejane is located in a Malaria area. Conservation levies are applicable.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"fact-heading\\">\\r\\n<h4><strong>RESERVATION AND CONTACT DETAILS<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"fact-text reserve\\">\\r\\n<p>PO Box 95, Hectorspruit, 1230, South Africa<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>T:<\\/strong> + 27 (0)13 792 7000 \\u2013 <strong>F:<\\/strong> + 27 (0)13 792 7020 \\u2013 <strong>E:<\\/strong> reservations@mjejaneriverlodge.co.za \\u2013 <strong>W:<\\/strong> www.mjejaneriverlodge.co.za<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>RESERVATION DETAILS:<\\/em><\\/strong> <strong>T:<\\/strong> + 27 (0)11 516 4367 <strong>| E:<\\/strong> res@extraordinary.co.za\\/ res1@extraordinary.co.za<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"2","created":"2014-12-20 03:55:44","created_by":"939","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-12-20 05:11:10","modified_by":"939","checked_out":"939","checked_out_time":"2014-12-20 05:10:38","publish_up":"2014-12-20 03:55:44","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\